{"id":"Ghost__Post__5f7e32231a93b603e3f7656e","title":"Particl Project Status Report: August 29th, 2017","slug":"particl-project-status-report-august-29th-2017-be1155bee282","featured":false,"feature_image":null,"excerpt":"\nDevelopment Update\n","custom_excerpt":"\nDevelopment Update\n","visibility":"public","created_at_pretty":"29 Aug 2017","published_at_pretty":"29 Aug 2017","updated_at_pretty":"27 Oct 2020","created_at":"2017-08-29T00:00:00.000+00:00","published_at":"2017-08-29T00:00:00.000+00:00","updated_at":"2020-10-27T18:19:55.000+00:00","meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"og_description":null,"og_image":null,"og_title":null,"twitter_description":null,"twitter_image":null,"twitter_title":null,"authors":[{"name":"dros","slug":"dros","url":"https://edit.particl.news/author/dros/","bio":null,"cover_image":null,"profile_image":null,"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":null,"coverImageSharp":null,"profileImageSharp":null}],"primary_author":{"name":"dros","slug":"dros","url":"https://edit.particl.news/author/dros/","bio":null,"cover_image":null,"profile_image":null,"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":null,"coverImageSharp":null,"profileImageSharp":null},"primary_tag":{"name":"Development Updates","slug":"dev-updates","url":"https://edit.particl.news/tag/dev-updates/","description":"See a blockchain-powered autonomous internet marketplace wunderkind grow. You make a difference with Particl.","feature_image":null,"meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public","featureImageSharp":null},"tags":[{"name":"Development Updates","slug":"dev-updates","url":"https://edit.particl.news/tag/dev-updates/","description":"See a blockchain-powered autonomous internet marketplace wunderkind grow. You make a difference with Particl.","feature_image":null,"meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public","featureImageSharp":null}],"plaintext":"Development Update\nStatus Reporting\nhttps://particl.io/status-report/\n\nIn our last project update post we revealed\n[https://particl.news/part-roadmap-v-1-1-e15f1b3c63a] the latest version of our\nroadmap and hinted at a new section for our website aimed at providing more\ntransparency in our development process. Below is a summary of what is keeping\nus busy. More detail can be found on the website\n[https://particl.io/status-report/].\n\n⏰ What are we busy with\n- Release of GUI TestNet\n— UI Integration\n\n— GUI Components\n\n- Particl Market Place\n— Current Bootstrap to Material migration\n\n— Market Place GUI Designs\n\n- Particl Copay based App\n- Particl Core\n— Backend conversion from Bitcoin 0.14 to Bitcoin 0.15 investigation\n\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n☑️ Waiting for review\n- GUI Components\n— Menu Animations\n\n— RPC Service\n\n— HD wallet import and generate mnemonic seed\n\n— Transaction Page — Design review\n\n— App-Password / unlock modal\n\n— GUI functionality bugs\n\n— GUI Modal Bugs\n\n— Daemon Modal\n\n— Syncing Modal to show connected peers\n\n- Particl Market Place\n— Initial category listing\n\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n🏁 Wrapped up\n- Release Particl roadmap\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n🌟 What’s on the Horizon\n- Particl Marketplace\n— Marketplace Categories\n\n— Establish Marketplace Codebase\n\n— Database Design\n\n— Messaging (Daemon/Core) — Paid messages / Listing fee\n\n— Functions (Backend)\n\n— GUI Design\n\n— GUI Integration (API Service + Consuming)\n\n— P2P Marketplace Governance\n\nThank you\n\nParticl Team","html":"<h3 id=\"development-update\">Development Update</h3><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://edit.particl.news/content/images/downloaded_images/Particl-Project-Status-Report--August-29th--2017/1-rnB9Qjp1ZvkFcFS4yhDCfQ.jpeg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt></figure><h2 id=\"status-reporting\">Status Reporting</h2><p><a href=\"https://particl.io/status-report/\">https://particl.io/status-report/</a></p><p>In our last project update post we <a href=\"https://particl.news/part-roadmap-v-1-1-e15f1b3c63a\">revealed</a> the latest version of our roadmap and hinted at a new section for our website aimed at providing more transparency in our development process. Below is a summary of what is keeping us busy. More detail can be found on the <a href=\"https://particl.io/status-report/\">website</a>.</p><h2 id=\"-what-are-we-busy-with\">⏰ What are we busy with</h2><h3 id=\"-release-of-gui-testnet\"><strong>- Release of GUI TestNet</strong></h3><p><em>— UI Integration</em></p><p><em>— GUI Components</em></p><h3 id=\"-particl-market-place\"><strong>- Particl Market Place</strong></h3><p><em>— Current Bootstrap to Material migration</em></p><p><em>— Market Place GUI Design</em>s</p><h3 id=\"-particl-copay-based-app\"><strong>- Particl Copay based App</strong></h3><h3 id=\"-particl-core\"><strong>- Particl Core</strong></h3><p><em>— Backend conversion from Bitcoin 0.14 to Bitcoin 0.15 investigation</em></p><hr><h2 id=\"-waiting-for-review\">☑️ Waiting for review</h2><h3 id=\"-gui-components\"><strong>- GUI Components</strong></h3><p><em>— Menu Animations</em></p><p><em>— RPC Service</em></p><p><em>— HD wallet import and generate mnemonic seed</em></p><p><em>— Transaction Page — Design review</em></p><p><em>— App-Password / unlock modal</em></p><p><em>— GUI functionality bugs</em></p><p><em>— GUI Modal Bugs</em></p><p><em>— Daemon Modal</em></p><p><em>— Syncing Modal to show connected peers</em></p><h3 id=\"-particl-market-place-1\"><strong>- Particl Market Place</strong></h3><p><em>— Initial category listing</em></p><hr><h2 id=\"-wrapped-up\">🏁 Wrapped up</h2><h3 id=\"-release-particl-roadmap\"><strong>- Release Particl roadmap</strong></h3><hr><h2 id=\"-what-s-on-the-horizon\">🌟 What’s on the Horizon</h2><h3 id=\"-particl-marketplace\"><strong>- Particl Marketplace</strong></h3><p><em>— Marketplace Categories</em></p><p><em>— Establish Marketplace Codebase</em></p><p><em>— Database Design</em></p><p><em>— Messaging (Daemon/Core) — Paid messages / Listing fee</em></p><p><em>— Functions (Backend)</em></p><p><em>— GUI Design</em></p><p><em>— GUI Integration (API Service + Consuming)</em></p><p><em>— P2P Marketplace Governance</em></p><p>Thank you</p><p>Particl Team\n\n</p>","url":"https://edit.particl.news/particl-project-status-report-august-29th-2017-be1155bee282/","canonical_url":null,"uuid":"a1da6079-00cb-4046-9325-853fb6934bbb","codeinjection_foot":null,"codeinjection_head":null,"codeinjection_styles":null,"comment_id":"5f7e32231a93b603e3f7656e","reading_time":1,"childHtmlRehype":{"html":"<h3 id=\"development-update\">Development Update</h3><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"/glink/downloaded_images/Particl-Project-Status-Report--August-29th--2017/1-rnB9Qjp1ZvkFcFS4yhDCfQ.jpeg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\"></figure><h2 id=\"status-reporting\">Status Reporting</h2><p><a href=\"https://particl.io/status-report/\">https://particl.io/status-report/</a></p><p>In our last project update post we <a href=\"https://particl.news/part-roadmap-v-1-1-e15f1b3c63a\">revealed</a> the latest version of our roadmap and hinted at a new section for our website aimed at providing more transparency in our development process. Below is a summary of what is keeping us busy. More detail can be found on the <a href=\"https://particl.io/status-report/\">website</a>.</p><h2 id=\"-what-are-we-busy-with\">⏰ What are we busy with</h2><h3 id=\"-release-of-gui-testnet\"><strong>- Release of GUI TestNet</strong></h3><p><em>— UI Integration</em></p><p><em>— GUI Components</em></p><h3 id=\"-particl-market-place\"><strong>- Particl Market Place</strong></h3><p><em>— Current Bootstrap to Material migration</em></p><p><em>— Market Place GUI Design</em>s</p><h3 id=\"-particl-copay-based-app\"><strong>- Particl Copay based App</strong></h3><h3 id=\"-particl-core\"><strong>- Particl